Deus Factum was helping with a Friday night raid. The posting guild is a smaller guild, on their first Fear raid. The posting guild had 20 people, had a few other guests(2 or 3) and then invited 7 Deus Factum people. The make up of the raid was a high number of first timers and many lower level Toons(46-49th lvl). This conforms to the 2/3 rule perfectly...<br>
<br>
But - Cazic was up...<br>
