<br>
This is a game that is played Real time with Real people who have Real jobs.<br>
<br>
It is 100% unfair to the big brother guild to have to kill cazic after the guild in the plane finally realizes at 1:00 AM EST that they cannot kill Cazic and therefore need to call in help.<br>
<br>
My proposal was simple to the utmost extreme.  It does not hinder the late night people and it does not hinder the euro people who play hella early in the morning.  It simply guarantees that the GODS GO DOWN in a timely manner.<br>
<br>
8:30 - 9:00 PM EST.  Someone for the &quot;council&quot; who has a ton of knowledge on fear and the guilds of the rathe zones into fear.  At that point in time they &quot;scout&quot; (either in /tells or /ooc,etc) to find out how far the guild(s) are at in fear and how many people,etc are in the zone.<br>
<br>
If it does not look like the people WILL kill the god then they can ask the other people from the &quot;council&quot; online to vote to make the determination if the big brother guild needs to be called in.<br>
<br>
SoT starting at 10am doesn't matter.  KIC starting at 8:00 PM does not matter.  What matters is track record / # people in the zone / clearing pattern, efficiency.<br>
<br>
If you can kill cazic and it does appear you will kill him (5:00 EST for all anyone cares..the issue is only that he dies) then nada happens.<br>
<br>
If it does not appear that you can get to him (24 people and draco still up,etc type scenario) then the person asks for a vote to be called and if determined that the big brother guild for that plane is needed they assemble and go in while it is still early enough to accomplish stuff and get to bed at a reasonable time for everyone involved.<br>
<br>
The 9:00 time frame that I stated was simply the cut off time for the determination to take place.  There are a myriad of guilds that are insane and have alot of High School or College kids that can stay up till 5:00 in the morning to kill Cazic and they deserve every right to him.  But the guilds who think they can but don't want to realize that they simply don't have the firepower to do it in a reasonable amount of time have to be overridden for the entire server to be able to get their FA's.<br>
<br>
Every day that cazic / inny stay up is 1 more day until they respawn barring server crashes which means longer and longer that we all have to wait on getting our FA's.<br>
<br>
-Howard<br>
